{"tid":2346813,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 墨西哥餡餅 配牛油果醬、蕃茄莎莎","createTime":"2020-12-30T13:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T05:29:28.000Z","uid":260581,"like":63,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1198a7cb9bd69cd600e8090648c91a50b46caf","tid":2346813,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCze3dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCze3dc.jpg&h=216e8e30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQ2gw6y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQ2gw6y.jpg&h=eb2cb251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買個熟d既牛油果黎整，㩒下佢就知熟唔熟，好熟望落去紫黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGuacamole用左牛油果，洋蔥，孜然粉，少少蒜蓉，鹽同青檸撈均<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0dZ3b7q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0dZ3b7q.jpg&h=a85e378c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個salsa有d核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面有蕃茄，洋蔥，芫荽，鹽同青檸<br />\n<br />\n洋蔥我用紫洋蔥係因為冇咁苦同帶甜味<br />\n切粒後浸冰水，浸味會冇咁澀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u2EuR8u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu2EuR8u.jpg&h=b75aa48e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個雞我落左蒜，孜然粉，cayenne,paprika 同鹽，<br />\n我唔記落oregano <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係煮雞胸果陣扔埋落去慢煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUNz3fM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUNz3fM.jpg&h=239af44d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eiAYLt7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeiAYLt7.jpg&h=da52b287&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrC4F2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrC4F2s.jpg&h=a3224814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係個平底鑊準備少少油，放tortilla 落去加芝士<br />\n冚埋佢咁慢慢烘溶d芝士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後加d炒過既紅椒粒同洋蔥粒<br />\n就可以落肉繼續慢火烘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一個落左雞，一個係上次塊斧頭扒d肉<br />\n因為仲未食曬，所以整兩款口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FepKF3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFepKF3r.jpg&h=44576390&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3KCgBN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3KCgBN.jpg&h=0cb3458d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一個墨西哥既quesadilla <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋guacamole, salsa, sour cream <br />\n一啖咬落去，一次感受幾隻味<br />\n好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b76404128421e5a2df76d1220ef44763aed556","tid":2346813,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"57a5adef94bb694dbeff2f77662841826405bbc4","tid":2346813,"uid":239860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58b76404128421e5a2df76d1220ef44763aed556","tid":2346813,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:47:10.000Z","msg":"終於1到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd14015b7fd20e0003aa98a89edbb9da6f9684bf","tid":2346813,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57a5adef94bb694dbeff2f77662841826405bbc4","tid":2346813,"uid":239860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58b76404128421e5a2df76d1220ef44763aed556","tid":2346813,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:47:10.000Z","msg":"終於1到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:47:35.000Z","msg":"夜晚冇乜人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2153b6ee20bcf0749e2589bcb065155cee9e7f41","tid":2346813,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"夾牛肉好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個牛油果大啲定你個二頭大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw香港牛油果好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97406639f22da809474c885658e6d68a022d629a","tid":2346813,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:48:54.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c389bc827d2a4606faf2550dce67d12e604f1a34","tid":2346813,"uid":260581,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33OC06m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33OC06m.jpg&h=4bd18d33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4nssDS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4nssDS2.jpg&h=3ca34006&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMNkero.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMNkero.jpg&h=eb696af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我撚廚係個三文魚蒟蒻麵<br />\n落左d沙律汁加隻慢煮蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe6f06c2055af89f0c6e591973032ffdc18c24d","tid":2346813,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2153b6ee20bcf0749e2589bcb065155cee9e7f41","tid":2346813,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"夾牛肉好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個牛油果大啲定你個二頭大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw香港牛油果好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"我冇牛油果咁大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果日行market, 特價做緊6蚊個<br />\n我覺得麻麻，最後去超市買<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個d肉大概250g<br />\n買左20蚊hkd<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53c0102a7780986a22292c82a7c0d5e9cbfef1d","tid":2346813,"uid":268868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fbeb0112a20cdf6dfeaec0a69280370392e2a6","tid":2346813,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97406639f22da809474c885658e6d68a022d629a","tid":2346813,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:48:54.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:55:10.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係<br />\n今日係low carb day, 得60g 都可以食呢d<br />\n我覺得好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b41ac677d11fd9468a1b4caeeea80a4e42e4d7","tid":2346813,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"香港啲牛油狗好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339a3e1c5628863b2c9cde60b0a70c3fe851208b","tid":2346813,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"禾今晚都食咗芋絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加白菜仔同白切雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0ddab4a4093ba7b15f6b40ee9ef07444087b10","tid":2346813,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e53c0102a7780986a22292c82a7c0d5e9cbfef1d","tid":2346813,"uid":268868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T14:00:21.000Z","msg":"跟住整，唔難整係煩少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05130baa846b662108e9c91337054fb00d80b977","tid":2346813,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a4b41ac677d11fd9468a1b4caeeea80a4e42e4d7","tid":2346813,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"香港啲牛油狗好難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-